quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,28,"Inform them that the water is to be shared out between them, each drinking by turn.´"
  54,29,They called on their companion and he set to it and hamstrung her
  54,30,How terrible were My punishment and warnings
  54,31,We sent a single Blast against them and they were just like a thatcher´s reeds
  54,32,We have made the Qur´an easy to remember. But is there any rememberer there
  54,33,The people of Lut denied the warnings
  54,34,"We unleashed a sudden squall of stones against all of them, except the family of Lut, who We rescued before dawn"
  54,35,It was a blessing direct from Our presence. That is how We recompense those who give thanks
  54,36,He warned them of Our onslaught but they dismissed the warnings
  54,37,"They even wanted to seduce his guests! So We put out their eyes: ´Taste My punishment and warnings!´"
  54,38,Early morning brought them enduring punishment
  54,39,´Taste My punishment and warnings!´
  54,40,We have made the Qur´an easy to remember But is there any rememberer there
  54,41,Warnings came to Pharaoh´s people
  54,42,"They dismissed every one of Our Signs and so We seized them with the seizing of One who is Almighty, All-Powerful"
  54,43,Are your kuffar better than those peoples´? Or have you been given exemption in the Books
  54,44,"Or do they say, ´We are an assembly who will win´"
  54,45,The assembly will be routed and will turn their backs in flight
  54,46,In fact the Hour is their promised appointment and the Hour is more disastrous and bitter
  54,47,The evildoers are indeed misguided and insane
  54,48,"on the Day that they are dragged face-first into the Fire: ´Taste the scorching touch of Saqar!´"
  54,49,We have created all things in due measure